=20
Enron Poland a strong position in the developing wholesale energy market.  =
In=20
the next two to three weeks, we expect to receive a cross-border trading=20
license covering gas imports that are further regulated under the Polish=20
Energy Law Ordinance on Gas Import Diversification.

