to=20
initiate the planning process for its first UK offshore wind farm, located =
at=20
Gunfleet Sands, 7km from Clacton-upon-Sea in Essex.  Construction is expect=
ed=20
to start towards the end of 2002, with the wind farm of 30 turbines being=
